textAnnotations.description:
Tangle-Free Flagpole
Your flag flies free, unfurled, not wrapped around the pole
Top flagpole section spins
on ball bearings, and,
together with gravity.
keeps your flag waving
free, even in wind.
Bracket adjusts a full 180°
to let you position the pole
and flag at any angle.
wwww.china raleronline. com
Sturdy, non-bending
aluminum pole has thick
walls
finish, and is topped with
a gleaming metallic
durable white
ball finial.
